===Description===
pyInstrumentation is an object-oriented library for connecting to serial, usb, and rs232 busses with python programs.  The code is meant to be written in an simplistic and straightforward way to help even non-programmers connect to their instrumentation for automated data analysis and acquisition.  Equipment that has been verified to work with pyInstrumentation include:

===List of Compatible Hardware===

====Microcontrollers====
Arduino UNO

====Function Generators====
Agilent 33210A

====Oscilloscopes====
Agilent DSOX2004A